data.description: Incredible INVESTMENT opportunity! Currently grossing nearly $200,000 per year as a short term rental! This single family home, turned triplex, creates great flexibility for short term rentals and keeps this property rented and cash flowing at all times. The house has been meticulously updated within the last few years, including a new roof, 3 new HVAC units, a new dock, and all the furnishings, decor and pleasantries needed to offer this as a turnkey short term rental. Each of the 3 units features a separate entrance, its own HVAC, a full kitchen with everything needed for your guests' comfort, separate laundry and a bathroom, in addition to 1 or 2 bedrooms (depending on which unit). Guests can also choose to rent the entire first floor, making it a 3 bedroom 2 bath, or the entire house, which is a 5 bedroom 3 bathroom home.     This nearly half acre property with 122 ft of Braden River frontage features a dock, a tiki bar with a refrigerator and a kegerator, a firepit and comes with two kayaks and a paddleboat. An electrical box with 50 amp or 30 amp hookup for an RV creates opportunity for additional income from RV parking, or even event venue rental with food trucks.    Located off of SR 70 near I-75, the close proximity of this property to UTC, Nathan Benderson Park, and Lakewood Ranch as well as our beaches and downtown Bradenton, brings guests in at all times of the year and throughout the week and the weekends. The home is fully equipped with everything your guests need to enjoy this little piece of Old Florida.    Sale of property will include AirBnB listing as well as all future bookings.
